import {
  IonButton,
  IonCol,
  IonGrid,
  IonInput,
  IonItem,
  IonLabel,
  IonRow,
} from "@ionic/react";
import React from "react";

const AdminForm: React.FC<{ buttonName: string, name: string, surname: string, cellNum: string, password: string }> = (props, {name, surname, cellNum, password}) => {
  return (
    <IonGrid>
      <IonRow>
        <IonCol>
          <IonItem>
            <IonLabel position="floating">Name</IonLabel>
            <IonInput type="text" value ={name}></IonInput>
          </IonItem>
        </IonCol>
      </IonRow>
      <IonRow>
        <IonCol>
          <IonItem>
            <IonLabel position="floating">Surname</IonLabel>
            <IonInput type="text" value ={surname}></IonInput>
          </IonItem>
        </IonCol>
      </IonRow>
      <IonRow>
        <IonCol>
          <IonItem>
            <IonLabel position="floating">Cell Number</IonLabel>
            <IonInput type="text" value ={cellNum}></IonInput>
          </IonItem>
        </IonCol>
      </IonRow>
      <IonRow>
        <IonCol>
          <IonItem>
            <IonLabel position="floating">Password</IonLabel>
            <IonInput type="password" value ={password}></IonInput>
          </IonItem>
        </IonCol>
      </IonRow>
      <IonRow>
        <IonCol>
          <IonItem>
            <IonLabel position="floating">Confrim Password</IonLabel>
            <IonInput type="password" value ={password}></IonInput>
          </IonItem>
        </IonCol>
      </IonRow>
      <IonRow>
        <IonCol>
          <IonButton href="/signIn" type="submit" expand="block">
            {props.buttonName}
          </IonButton>
        </IonCol>
      </IonRow>
    </IonGrid>
  );
};

export default AdminForm;
